        <prompt>What was the primary goal of the Enforcement Acts of 1870-1871?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">To protect African American voting rights from Klan violence</option>
            <option letter="b">To regulate commerce</option>
            <option letter="c">To establish schools</option>
            <option letter="d">To manage land distribution</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Enforcement Acts were passed to protect African American voting rights from Ku Klux Klan violence and intimidation in the South.</explanation>
