    <question>
        <prompt>What was the significance of Blanche K. Bruce?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Second African American U.S. Senator and former slave</option>
            <option letter="b">Leader of the Freedmen's Bureau</option>
            <option letter="c">Confederate general</option>
            <option letter="d">White House staff member</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Blanche K. Bruce was the second African American U.S. Senator and the first former slave to serve a full Senate term, representing Mississippi.</explanation>
